1098
01:08:08,880 --> 01:08:09,960
Hello.

1099
01:08:09,960 --> 01:08:11,920
Hi, it's Elizabeth.

1100
01:08:13,679 --> 01:08:15,159
Calling to apologize?

1101
01:08:15,159 --> 01:08:17,880
No, look, I need
to ask you a favor.

1102
01:08:17,880 --> 01:08:20,439
Well, word on the street is
