to anyone.

1110
01:08:35,000 --> 01:08:36,920
No talking.

1111
01:08:36,920 --> 01:08:39,159
And I told them
you're my brother.

1112
01:08:39,159 --> 01:08:40,920
- You what?
- I had to.

1113
01:08:40,920 --> 01:08:44,359
Just please go and get him
and bring him back.

1114
01:08:44,359 --> 01:08:46,680
Just get in
and get out.

1115
01:08:46,680 --> 01:08:49,920
Pick him up, bring him back,
do not talk. Got it.

1116
01:08:53,960 --> 01:08:56,199
Hey, buddy.

1117
01:08:56,199 --> 01:08:58,800
Your mom asked me
to come and get you.

1118
01:08:58,800 --> 01:09:00,680
Okay.

1119
01:09:02,800 --> 01:09:05,159
Are you here
for Alexander?

1120
01:09:05,159 --> 01:09:06,319
