1134
01:09:38,159 --> 01:09:40,079
Where are my...?

1135
01:09:40,079 --> 01:09:42,000
If you would...

1136
01:09:42,000 --> 01:09:43,920
That's nice.

1137
01:09:57,760 --> 01:09:59,039
