1145
01:10:17,159 --> 01:10:19,720
If one of the other students
is hurt or upset,

1146
01:10:19,720 --> 01:10:22,640
Alexander's always the first
one to show them comfort.

1147
01:10:22,640 --> 01:10:25,279
He's quite empathetic.

1148
01:10:25,279 --> 01:10:27,520
And empathetic is good.

1149
01:10:27,520 --> 01:10:29,840
- Great.
- But in some of the other areas...

1150
01:10:29,840 --> 01:10:32,479
Empathy, reading,
friendship... what else is there?

1151
01:10:32,479 --> 01:10:34,560
Well, math.

1152
01:10:34,560 --> 01:10:36,399
He's far behind
the other students.

1153
01:10:36,399 --> 01:10:38,039
He still struggles
with arithmetic

1154
01:10:38,039 --> 01:10:41,159
while the other students
have moved on to multiplication.

1155
01:10:43,520 --> 01:10:45,079
Well, you're the teacher.
Aren't you supposed to be able

1156
01:10:45,079 --> 01:10:47,439
