time to one student.

1159
01:10:55,119 --> 01:10:56,840
And Alexander
still needs to learn

1160
01:10:56,840 --> 01:10:59,119
our very first lesson.

1161
01:11:02,239 --> 01:11:05,479
And he's also...
oh, how do I say this?

1162
01:11:07,279 --> 01:11:10,000
Well, immature.

1163
