tell jokes while she's talking.

1191
01:12:23,359 --> 01:12:25,439
- Okay.
- Oh, and by the way,

1192
01:12:25,439 --> 01:12:28,199
If she asks...
I'm your uncle.

1193
01:12:28,199 --> 01:12:30,439
My name is Zebulon.
Zebulon...

