1214
01:13:48,600 --> 01:13:51,319
Yes, he was.

1215
01:13:51,319 --> 01:13:52,880
Do you miss him?

1216
01:13:52,880 --> 01:13:54,640
Very much.

1217
01:13:54,640 --> 01:13:56,920
Yes, I do.

1218
01:13:56,920 --> 01:13:58,680
Me too.

1219
01:14:01,000 --> 01:14:03,319
