1230
01:14:43,720 --> 01:14:44,800
Nothing.

1231
01:14:51,119 --> 01:14:53,199
Come on, you.
Did you have fun?

1232
01:14:53,199 --> 01:14:55,760
Hamburgers?

1233
01:14:55,760 --> 01:14:58,079
