the man on the phone,

1250
01:16:34,920 --> 01:16:36,479
and this is
what it did for you.

1251
01:16:41,119 --> 01:16:43,199
So I may as well
go ahead and drink.

1252
01:16:43,199 --> 01:16:46,319
That's not what I meant.

1253
01:16:48,359 --> 01:16:51,159
Congratulations, Arlen.

1254
01:16:51,159 --> 01:16:52,840
You can have
your life back now.

1255
01:16:52,840 --> 01:16:54,800
Isn't that
what you want?

1256
01:16:58,079 --> 01:17:00,079
Get out.

1257
01:17:31,640 --> 01:17:33,960
- Hello.
- Hello, Arlen,

1258
01:17:33,960 --> 01:17:36,560
