1262
01:17:44,399 --> 01:17:46,279
What did you say to her?

1263
01:17:46,279 --> 01:17:48,760
Nothing.

1264
01:17:48,760 --> 01:17:51,720
"Kids develop," you know,
"friendship, reading,"

1265
01:17:51,720 --> 01:17:53,560
maybe something
