1268
01:17:58,039 --> 01:18:01,199
Oh, well, that's
totally amazing.

1269
01:18:01,199 --> 01:18:04,479
Thank you, thank you,
thank you, thank you.

1270
01:18:04,479 --> 01:18:06,359
Just when I give up
